net.atos.kawwaportal.components.tree

Interface TreeModel<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of data in the tree
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTreeModel

    public interface TreeModel<T>
    A model for tree-oriented data used by the Tree component. The default implemention, DefaultTreeModel uses a ValueEncoder and a TreeModelAdapter to supply the underlying information.
    Since:
    5.3
    See Also:
    TreeSelectionModel
